        <item>
            <title>Samsung 推中階新「孖寶」Galaxy A35 + Galaxy A55　四色韓風 + 強化夜攝 + 定價更抵玩</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/21/samsung-launch-new-midlevel-galaxy-a35-a55-smartphone/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=samsung-launch-new-midlevel-galaxy-a35-a55-smartphone</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/21/samsung-launch-new-midlevel-galaxy-a35-a55-smartphone/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 13:00:10 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[galaxy]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy A35]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy A55]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[samsung]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1225587</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>雖然各手機品牌一向都是以旗艦手機來打響品牌，但如果講起穩定的使用體驗，以及相對抵玩來講，在現今這個經濟不算太好的時勢，中階機似乎才是各品牌的主戰場。Samsung 今日就宣佈推出全新的中階新機 Galaxy A35 及 Galaxy A55，定價比上代 A3 / A5 系更抵玩，同時又擁有不少由旗艦手機下放的功能。現在就讓筆者帶大家都記招現場看看吧。</p><h2>韓風設計四色外觀</h2><p>今次 Samsung 推出的兩部全新中階手機 Galaxy A35 及 Galaxy A55，前者規格相對較入門，機身設計亦較簡單，強化玻璃機背採用淨色設計，而用色亦偏向鮮艷淡色，韓風味道甚濃。機身採圓角及平面方正設計，大方美觀。機身不算很薄，而且偏闊，筆者試過單手操控有點勉強，但仍是可以的，幸好機身算輕，長時間使用也不算大問題。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225593" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01644-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01644-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01644.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225594" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01643-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01643-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01643.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次 Samsung 推出兩部中階新機 Galaxy A35（左）及 A55（右）兩者均採用強化玻璃作機背，而且熒幕及機背邊位均採用全平面設計，機背配色亦採十分韓風的少女風淨色風格。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225595" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01671-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01671-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01671.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲A35 / A55 均設有 4 種相同的機身顏色，分別是海軍藍、檸檬黃、冰川藍及丁香紫（左至右）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225597" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01619-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01619-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01619.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有些配色像丁香紫，在不同角度會隱約看到彩虹色，十分吸引。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225599" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01582-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01582-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01582.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225600" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01634-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01634-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01634.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲A35（第一張）及 A55（第二張）熒幕今代同樣增加至 6.6 吋，所以機身是比上代闊了一點。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225606" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01629-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01629-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01629.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於機身設計方面，A35 及 A55 機邊均採用平面設計，只是開關及音量鍵部分採用較出一點的設計，這與上代採用凸出曲邊設計是不同的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225605" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01623-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01623-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01623.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不過機邊設計方面，A35（左）就採用相對較平實的實色設計，而 A55（右）就加入了拉絲紋設計，感覺相對較高貴一點。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225602" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01594-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01594-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01594.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225603" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01596-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01596-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01596.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225604" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01595-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01595-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01595.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲由於熒幕大了，所以單手握機操控或打字時比上代是相對困難了，但如果手掌較大（像筆者），也仍算可勉強做到。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225607" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01627-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01627-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01627.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225608" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01628-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01628-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01628.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲兩部新機 SIM 卡槽均設於機頂，機底同樣設有內置喇叭及 USB-C 插槽。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225609" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01630-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01630-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01630-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而兩部新機的開關及音量鍵也同樣設於機身右側。</p><h2>中階基本配置未見新功能</h2><p>至於功能及配置上，A35 與 A55 基本上只是輕微替換上最新的硬件配置，分別內建 Exynos 1380（A35）/ 1480（A55）處理器、8GB（A35 / A55 低階版）/ 12GB（A55 高階版）RAM 及 128GB / 256GB 內存，與上代屬同級。顯示方面，就增大至採用 6.6 吋 2340 x 1080 解像度 120Hz 更新率 Infinity-O Super AMOLED 熒幕。相機方面，A35 及 A55 均採用三鏡頭主相機，主攝鏡及微距鏡均為 5,000 萬及 500 萬像素，而超廣角鏡方面，就分別為 800 萬像素（A35）及 1,200 萬像素（A55），當中 A55 與上代 A54 一樣，也支援黑夜亮攝功能，有助強化夜攝時的表現。至於前置鏡頭方面，A35 及 A55 支援像素就分別為 1,300 萬及 3,200 萬。由此可見，A35 及 A55，相比各自的上代 A34 及 A54，其實也只是小修小補的升級，未見太大驚喜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225610" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01646-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01646-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01646.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225611" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01650-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01650-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01650.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲A35（第一張）及 A55（第二張）分別採用 Exynos 1380 及 Exynos 1480 處理器，另外 A35 只配備了 8GB + 128GB / 256GB 規格，但 A55 除了有 8GB + 128GB 版本外，亦設有 12GB + 256GB 的較高階版本。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225612" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01645-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01645-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01645.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲電量方面兩機均內建了 5,000mAh 容量電池，絕對足夠用上一天以上。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225613" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01587-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01587-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01587.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225614" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01620-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01620-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01620.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225615" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01639-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01639-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01639.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲A35（第一張）及 A55（第二張）均採用了 3 鏡頭的主相機設計，兩機均內建了 5,000 萬像素主攝鏡及 500 萬像素微距鏡，而 A55 的超廣角鏡就支援 1,200 萬像素，相對 A35 的超廣角鏡就只支援至 800 萬像素。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225616" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01641-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01641-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01641.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲值得一提的是，只有較高階的 A55 才支援黑夜亮攝功能，A35 是不支援的。</p><h2>定價相對更抵玩</h2><p>功能上未見大新意，但定價就有一定驚喜。今代 Samsung 推出 Galaxy A35 及 Galaxy A55，兩機均設有海軍藍、冰川藍、檸檬黃及丁香紫 4 隻機身顏色，定價分別為 $2,698 起及 $3,298 起，A35 相比上代起步價便宜了 $300，A55 相比上代更是便宜了足足 $700！而 A55 即使高階版本，也比上代便宜了 $300，但今代卻加入 12GB RAM，比上代多了 4GB RAM，所以同樣是更抵玩。換言之，雖然今代給予用家「換湯不換藥」的感覺，但定價抵玩得多，也是頗吸引的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225592" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01658-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01658-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01658.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>至於開售詳情方面，Samsung 將會明日（3 月 22 日）至 27 日推出早鳥優惠，優惠期內入手也會有與旅行有關的贈品，還可獲贈 Galaxy Buds FE 真無線降噪耳機，而以往的 Trade-in 回贈優惠及 Trade-in 價格保證優惠仍有提供。而兩部全新中階手機，就會在 3 月 28 日正式公開發售。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225617" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01669-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01669-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dsc01669-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>售價：$2,698（A35 8 + 128）；$2,998（A35 8 + 256）；$3,298（A55 8 + 128）；$3,698（A55 12 + 256）</strong><br /><strong>查詢：Samsung（3698 4698）</strong></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/18/samsung-s24-%e7%8f%be%e5%a0%b4%e6%b8%ac%e8%a9%a6%e9%96%8b%e7%ae%b1%e3%80%80%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e6%9c%80%e6%84%9b-7-%e5%a4%a7%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Samsung S24 現場測試開箱影片　港人最愛 7 大功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/18/samsung-s24-ultra-first-look/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra　外形　手感　AI 功能　操作體驗初步評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/21/samsung-to-launch-ai-chips-to-challenge-nvidia-others-mach-1-chips-to-launch-in-early-2025/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Samsung 公佈全新 AI 項目   Mach-1 晶片 2025 年推出</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/21/samsung-launch-new-midlevel-galaxy-a35-a55-smartphone/mobile-phone/">Samsung 推中階新「孖寶」Galaxy A35 + Galaxy A55　四色韓風 + 強化夜攝 + 定價更抵玩</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
